Interface BlenderKey.FeaturesToLoad

  • Enclosing class:
    BlenderKey
    Deprecated. 
    this interface is deprecated and is not used anymore; to ensure the loading models consistency everything must be loaded because in blender one feature might depend on another

    @Deprecated
public static interface BlenderKey.FeaturesToLoad
    This interface describes the features of the scene that are to be loaded.
